overview: The world is his stage, all eyes are on him. You want a piece, and he knows it. Get seduced by Jessy Ares in a Command Performance with fellow TitanMen exclusives Dario Beck, Jesse Jackman and Marco Wilson. They all lead a group of eager talent ready to fuck like a rock star.  Beefy office mates Jesse Jackman and Roman Wright work out their frustrations with a flip fuck that has their hairy bods sweating.  At the gym, a song in the shower from Dario Beck enraptures smooth Cavin Knight—who offers his warm mouth and tight hole in appreciation.  The recording studio heats up as the duet between Jessy Ares and Marco Wilson explodes, with Junior Stellano and Wilfried Knight soon joining them—their moans making memorable music.
title: Command Performance
